description:
Support The Pack Here
https://tr.ee/MinimalNights3

In this video, Iâ€™m breaking down some of the most sought-after sounds in Minimal / Deep Tech right now.

I went deep Spotify playlists, DJ sets, and the Beatport Top 100â€”pulled the tones that keep showing up, then rebuilt them in Serum 2 so you can use them in your own tracks.

Serum 2â€™s granular section took everything up a notch: chord stabs with extra texture and depth, basslines that feel juicier, and those organ-style basses that just hit different. Overall, the synth made it possible to push these remakes further and turn them into a pack of sounds that actually works in real sessions.
